title: Orb (disambiguation)
content:
Orb may refer to:

  • A circle.
  • A sphere.

Items[edit | edit source]

  • Materials to create battlestaves:
    • Unpowered orb
    • Air orb
    • Water orb
    • Earth orb
    • Fire orb
  • Orbs that enhance the nightmare staff:
    • Eldritch orb
    • Harmonised orb
    • Volatile orb
  • Commorb, used in the Wanted! quest.
  • Commorb v2, used in The Slug Menace quest.
  • Dead orb, an unobtainable item.
  • Light orb, and its empty version.
  • Locator orb, and its inert version, used in the Dragon Slayer II quest.
  • Magical orb, used in the The Hand in the Sand quest.
  • Mysterious orb (Client of Kourend), used in the Client of Kourend quest.
  • Mysterious orb (X Marks the Spot), used in the X Marks the Spot quest.
  • Oculus orb
  • Orb, used in the Mage Training Arena minigame.
  • Orb, used in the Devious Minds quest.
  • Orb of light, used in the Underground Pass quest.
  • Orb of protection, and its doubled-up version, used in the Tree Gnome Village quest.
  • Scrying orb, used in the Enter the Abyss miniquest.

Other[edit | edit source]

  • Enchantment spells:
    • Charge Air Orb
    • Charge Water Orb
    • Charge Earth Orb
    • Charge Fire Orb
  • Data orb, part of the interface.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
